entries.name: json_create(object)
entries.desc: Deserializes JSON string by converting year y, month m, day d, hour H, minute M, second S, offset of and Day of Calendar Reform sg to DateTime.

entries.name: as_json(*)
entries.desc: Returns a hash, that will be turned into a JSON object and represent this object.
